symboltable

Class SymbolTable.Symbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • symboltable.SymbolTable.Symbol
  • Enclosing class:
    SymbolTable

    public class SymbolTable.Symbol
extends java.lang.Object
    A data structure to store each symbol in the symbol table. A symbol always has a name and a kind. Depending on the type of symbol different constructors will be called. The different constructors take in different information and store it in a symbol object. Class is protected so it can be accessed for testing.
